### Testing on Multi frameworks
	Open project file in editor and add new framework against you want to test your test cases
	<TargetFrameworks>netcoreapp2.2;net472</TargetFrameworks>

	Test Exploror = use column or filter to see framework against each test cases

### Test case common initialization/Shared Context between Tests

### Exposing internal method  in separate test project
	
	> Step1: create AssemblyAttribute.cs in your source project
	> Step2: [assembly: InternalVisibileTo("test-project-name-space")]

### Test Adapters in visual studio

	*.TestAdapter.dll 
	
	From: Microsoft.TestPlatform.Object.Model

	ITestDiscoverer (Microsoft.VisualStudio.TestPlatform.Object.Model.dll)
	ITestExecutor (Microsoft.VisualStudio.TestPlatform.Object.Model.dll)

### Options - Real time test discovery
	-> Options-> Test -> General -> Checkbox (Real time test discovery )

	